          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Right-of-Way for American Drivers Act of 2015</b></p> <p>This bill repeals the transportation alternatives program. That program funds such projects as those for pedestrians and bicyclists, non-driver and disabled access to safe transportation, recreational trails and areas, land use in rights-of-way, and environmental mitigation (including protection of wildlife).</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2015-06-02T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
